lead_paragraph: European Champions Spain produced a dominant display to thrash South Korea 6-1 in Salzburg, Austria on Wednesday in their penultimate friendly before Euro 2016.

headline.print_headline: Nolito and Morata Fire Spain to Easy Win Over South Korea
